data.description: This bi-level gem offers everything you've been searching for and more. Nestled in the heart of picturesque Canon City, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven boasts truly outstanding views of the cityscape, Skyline Dr, and the majestic Sangre de Cristo mountains. As you step inside, you'll immediately be captivated by the wall of large windows and oversized patio doors that perfectly frame the breathtaking vistas, flooding the home with natural light and inviting the outdoors in. This home has been thoughtfully upgraded with Anderson windows, and a solar system, ensuring not only peace of mind but also relief from high energy costs. The heart of the home, the updated kitchen, is a chef's delight, featuring stainless steel appliances, solid surface countertops, and an inviting eat-in bar, perfect for casual dining or entertaining guests. With an attached 2-car garage, you'll never have to worry about parking or storage space. And when it's time to relax and unwind, step out onto one of the decks and soak in the panoramic views while enjoying your morning coffee or hosting al fresco dinners with friends and family. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to own a slice of paradise in Canon City. Schedule your showing today and make this stunning home yours before it's gone!
